Class SaleStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment.SaleStructure

  • public class SaleStructure
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the monthly details of the orders placed for a particular menu item. Contains the number of times a particular item was sold and the total revenue generated by each item.
